    </table>
  </div>

  <p class="muted" style="margin-top:4mm; font-size:8pt; line-height:1.65;">
    Third-party prices are indicative, set by each provider, and may change. Accounts are
    registered in your name so you retain full ownership of your app, data and infrastructure.
    We handle the setup of every service above as part of the launch process — at no extra charge.
  </p>
</section>

