<section class="page">
  <div class="sec-head">
    <div class="kicker">
      <span class="chip-no">→</span>
      <span class="eyebrow">Next steps</span>
    </div>
    <h2>From idea to launch</h2>
    <p class="lead">Here's the path we recommend to turn <%= app_name %> into a live product.</p>
  </div>

  <%
    steps = [
      ['Review this proposal', 'This week',  'Share it with your team — we\'re happy to walk through any section on a quick call.'],
      ['Discovery call',       '30 minutes', 'We align on vision, priorities and open questions, and refine the estimate where needed.'],
      ['Scope & agreement',    'Week 1',     'We lock the MVP scope, timeline and milestones, and sign a simple service agreement.'],
      ['Design sprint',        'Weeks 1–3',  'Wireframes and UI design for the core flows, reviewed and approved by you.'],
      ['Development & QA',     timeline_short.to_s.capitalize, 'Agile sprints with weekly demos, continuous testing and full visibility of progress.'],
      ['Launch & support',     'Go-live',    'Store submission, infrastructure setup and a dedicated support window after release.']
    ]
  %>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-label"><%= icon.call('route-square') %> The path, step by step</div>
    <% steps.each_with_index do |(title, time, desc), i| %>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="idx"><%= format('%02d', i + 1) %></div>
        <div class="body">
          <span class="t"><%= title %></span> — <%= desc %>
        </div>
        <div class="tail"><span class="chip <%= i < 2 ? 'a' : 'n' %> plain"><%= time %></span></div>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <div class="note green vgap">
    <div class="note-title"><%= icon.call('tick-circle') %> The takeaway</div>
    The scope is costed, the market is researched, and the build is phased so you can start
    small and grow. The next step is a 30-minute call — after that you'll have everything
    you need to decide.
  </div>

  <div class="cta-card">
    <h3>Ready to build <%= app_name %>?</h3>
    <p>Pick a slot that suits you and we'll walk through scope, timeline, and any open questions in a free 30-minute call — no commitment needed.</p>
    <a class="cta-btn" href="<%= booking_url %>"><%= icon.call('calendar-tick', 13) %> Schedule a call <span class="url"><%= booking_display %></span></a>
    <div class="contact">
      <span><%= icon.call('sms', 10) %> sales@tecaudex.com</span>
      <span><%= icon.call('global', 10) %> www.tecaudex.com</span>
      <span><%= icon.call('call', 10) %> © <%= year %> Tecaudex · Confidential</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

